#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.reset_index.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.reset\\_index"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:1 of
msgid "Generate a new DataFrame or Series with the index reset."
msgstr "生成一个新的 DataFrame 或 Series，并重置其索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:3 of
msgid ""
"This is useful when the index needs to be treated as a column, or when "
"the index is meaningless and needs to be reset to the default before "
"another operation."
msgstr ""
"当索引需要被当作一列处理，或者索引没有意义并需要在其他操作之前重置为"
"默认值时，这非常有用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:7 of
msgid ""
"For a Series with a MultiIndex, only remove the specified levels from the"
" index. Removes all levels by default."
msgstr ""
"对于具有 MultiIndex 的 Series，只移除索引中的指定层级。默认情况下移除所有"
"层级。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:10 of
msgid ""
"Just reset the index, without inserting it as a column in the new "
"DataFrame."
msgstr "仅重置索引，而不将其作为新 DataFrame 中的一列插入。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:13 of
msgid ""
"The name to use for the column containing the original Series values. "
"Uses ``self.name`` by default. This argument is ignored when `drop` is "
"True."
msgstr ""
"用于包含原始 Series 值的列的名称。默认使用 ``self.name``。当 `drop` 为 "
"True 时此参数将被忽略。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:17 of
msgid "Modify the Series in place (do not create a new object)."
msgstr "就地修改 Series（不创建新的对象）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:20 of
msgid ""
"When `drop` is False (the default), a DataFrame is returned. The newly "
"created columns will come first in the DataFrame, followed by the "
"original Series values. When `drop` is True, a `Series` is returned. In "
"either case, if ``inplace=True``, no value is returned."
msgstr ""
"当 `drop` 为 False（默认）时，返回一个 DataFrame。新建的列会出现在 "
"DataFrame 的最前面，后面跟着原始的 Series 值。当 `drop` 为 True 时，返回"
"一个 `Series`。无论哪种情况，如果 ``inplace=True``，则不会返回任何值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.reset_index`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:30 of
msgid "Analogous function for DataFrame."
msgstr "DataFrame 的类似函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:33 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:39 of
msgid "Generate a DataFrame with default index."
msgstr "生成一个具有默认索引的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:48 of
msgid "To specify the name of the new column use `name`."
msgstr "要指定新列的名称，请使用 `name`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:57 of
msgid "To generate a new Series with the default set `drop` to True."
msgstr "要生成一个带有默认设置的新 Series，请将 `drop` 设为 True。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:66 of
msgid ""
"To update the Series in place, without generating a new one set `inplace`"
" to True. Note that it also requires ``drop=True``."
msgstr ""
"要就地更新 Series 而不生成新的 Series，请将 `inplace` 设为 True。注意这还"
"需要 ``drop=True``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:77 of
msgid "The `level` parameter is interesting for Series with a multi-level index."
msgstr "`level` 参数对具有多级索引的 Series 很有用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:89 of
msgid "To remove a specific level from the Index, use `level`."
msgstr "要从索引中移除特定层级，请使用 `level`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.reset_index.series_reset_index:99 of
msgid "If `level` is not set, all levels are removed from the Index."
msgstr "如果未设置 `level`，则从索引中移除所有层级。"

